            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#JP">
                <p>[Of King Gelon]; of Queen Nereis; of Queen Philistis; of King Hieron; of Zeus Olympios; [----]; of Herakles the stout-hearted; [----]; [----] </p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The reading of cuneus 7 is generally agreed, although the visibility of the individual letters varies from one edition to the next. The missing divine names in 6, 8 and 9 are commonly suggested to be Hera, Kore and Demeter.</p>
            </div>
